Animation : 
1.Animation simply shows element in more attractive manner than usual manner.
2.Animation can be implemented on text, images and elements like div.
3.Animation uses @keyframes rule to implement Animation
  syntax : @keyframes animation_name{
                from{.....}
                to{.......}
            }

           @keyframes animation_name{
                0%{........}
                50%{.......}
                .....
                100%{......}
            }
4. Animation have some properties : 
    animation-name 
    animation-duration
    animation-iteration-count
    animation-timing-function
    animation-direction
    etc etc
 